      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in superlative condition and showing virtually no signs of prior ownership. The exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains in a state of pristine preservation, free from any wear or tactile degradation. Engineered for the most discerning enthusiast, this specimen has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity is absolute. This is an invitation to acquire a vehicle of rare distinction, offering an uncompromising driving experience that mirrors its initial delivery state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
